        "answer_count": 4,
        "title": "Java Map that is Multi Value and supports generics?",
        "body": "<p>I noticed that there is a <a href=\"http://commons.apache.org/collections/apidocs/org/apache/commons/collections/map/MultiValueMap.html\">MultiValueMap<\/a> from commons, however it doesn't support generics. Is there such a map that does?<\/p>\n",
